Package: python-snake-game
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, ${python3:Depends}, python3-pygame
Description: A simple snake game for Linux
 A fun and simple snake game written in Python using Pygame.
 Navigate the snake to eat food and grow longer while avoiding walls
 and colliding with yourself.
 .
 Use arrow keys to move, R to restart, Q to quit.
